::Primal Prime::

    "Cybertron?!" Prime said after the others had left. H=
e decided he needed to see for himself. He walked through the Gateway. On t=
he other side he was different. He was alot different, same paint job, most=
ly. Different body. (TM Optimus Primal in Prime colors, beast mode is blue =
though)
    He decided to see what his body could do.
    "Vehical Mode." P=
rime said thinking it would return him to a tank like mode, it didn't. Inst=
ead he changed to Beast mode and then his feet became a hover board. But it=
 was time to go back to Earth. He was in the air and flying, he truned and =
went through the Gateway. He came out on the other side still in his Cybert=
ron form.
    "Whatever, now I can fly," He said to himself. But that form =
didn't last. It did however add some new modes to Primal Prime. (Now he's f=
ull fleged Primal Prime, all 4 modes) Instead of falling he transformed to =
a flight mode. He dicided to go to the Embassy. Roaring off after the other=
 bots, he wanted to know what this is about.
